  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《flood of zombies》 is a survivor type shooting game, you will play as a soldier, in the countless zombie attacks to seek survival, collect resources, strengthen their own, destroy zombies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras/33238696af369cad50cfeaa94547f37e.avif?t=1741089614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras_big/33238696af369cad50cfeaa94547f37e.avif?t=1741089614 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, by killing zombies to gain experience, upgrade can strengthen weapons, unlock equipment, with the most reasonable plan, kill the most terrible BOSS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game provides dozens of weapons, auxiliary equipment, and characters, each role has different skills, is sure to bring you a rich play experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras/c166fe500bdf0b8847d4a09de26562ee.avif?t=1741089614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras_big/c166fe500bdf0b8847d4a09de26562ee.avif?t=1741089614 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are three maps in the game, each map has a unique zombie waiting for you to challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras/533f77213e5544aab6f19a859ee29e5d.avif?t=1741089614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras_big/533f77213e5544aab6f19a859ee29e5d.avif?t=1741089614 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《flood of zombies》 is a survivor type shooting game, you will play as a soldier, in the countless zombie attacks to seek survival, collect resources, strengthen their own, destroy zombies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras/33238696af369cad50cfeaa94547f37e.avif?t=1741089614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras_big/33238696af369cad50cfeaa94547f37e.avif?t=1741089614 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, by killing zombies to gain experience, upgrade can strengthen weapons, unlock equipment, with the most reasonable plan, kill the most terrible BOSS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game provides dozens of weapons, auxiliary equipment, and characters, each role has different skills, is sure to bring you a rich play experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras/c166fe500bdf0b8847d4a09de26562ee.avif?t=1741089614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras_big/c166fe500bdf0b8847d4a09de26562ee.avif?t=1741089614 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are three maps in the game, each map has a unique zombie waiting for you to challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras/533f77213e5544aab6f19a859ee29e5d.avif?t=1741089614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3347250/extras_big/533f77213e5544aab6f19a859ee29e5d.avif?t=1741089614 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
